*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
MODULE USER_COMMAND_0100 INPUT.

      CASE OK_CODE.
            WHEN 'SAVE'.
         PERFORM SAVE_DATA.
      ENDCASE.

      CLEAR OK_CODE.
ENDMODULE.
